 <a href=\"/best-background-check-services\">background checks</a> on Instant Checkmate are private. There is no way for anyone to know who you searched for. You don&#39;t even have to create an account. The only information you enter when you search is the name of the person you&#39;re searching for, your name and your email address.","Any transactions you make with Instant Checkmate are protected by Norton Security and a 128-bit encrypted connection, so your payment information remains secure. If you&#39;re worried about the safety of your own personal information, you can ask to have your information removed from Instant Checkmate on its opt-out page.","<strong>Is Instant Checkmate Free?</strong>","Searching for a report is free. You can see whether Instant Checkmate has any information available on the person you&#39;re looking for at no cost to you. The free information is limited to the city the person lives in and whether or not a background-check report is available.","Once Instant Checkmate gathers all the information and forms a report, it prompts you to enter your credit card or PayPal information to pay for a monthly subscription. One month of unlimited searches costs $22.86, less than what most other services charge for a single background check. You save even more when you buy more than one month of unlimited searching at a time.","If a person&#39;s background information is not available on public record, as arrest records are in some states, you may be required to pay an extra $20 fee to get access to this information in the report.","<strong>Who Uses Instant Checkmate?</strong>","Thousands of users have used Instant Checkmate to find old friends and make sure new friends are safe to be around. It&#39;s one of the most popular background check providers on the internet. If you&#39;re still not sure whether Instant Checkmate is right for you, you can read customer reviews online.","Next time your curiosity gets the better of you, Instant Checkmate is 